Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Video bridges the gap between survivors and audiences
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between seeing and changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At WITNESS the purpose of video is to get the story told
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the right people to see it and action taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WITNESS has been empowering women around the world for 17 years
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,partnering with organizations and working on issues impacting women and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From exposing the trafficking of women in eastern Europe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to advocating for women landmine victims in Senegal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to protecting our elderly from abuse, right here in the United States...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WITNESS changes lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women who have survived human rights abuses are speaking up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that others won't experience the same injustices.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violence against women in Zimbabwe is because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,women are becoming more and more involved in politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To try and to stop these women from involvement in politics
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they are beaten, they are sexually assaulted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,RAU decided to work with WITNESS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because it will give people a chance to watch the film
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then to see what is going on in Zimbabwe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Yemen, witnesses working with the Sisters Arab Forum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to advocate for the rights of minority "Akhdam" women
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The video was screened in Yemen to members
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of Parliament, journalists and civil society
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has unfortunately since been banned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WITNESS is working to have the ban lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Mexico, DUAL INJUSTICE tells the story of 19-year old Neyra
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who disappeared on her way home from school in 2003.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WITNESS recently met the mexican president and select government officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have since created a working group
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to end the disappearances and murders that have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,claimed the lives of over 450 girls and young women.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Macedonia, our WITNESS partner advocates
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to end violence and discrimination against women
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including sex workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violence and discrimination against women and girls
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is one of today's most pervasive human rights violations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WITNESS empowers those standing up for the rights of women
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to expose injustices, tell their stories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and create lasting change.
